title: Online interface for FET timetable scheduling system
description:
FET is open source free software for automatically scheduling the timetable of a school, high-school or university. It uses a fast and efficient timetabling algorithm. It is licensed under GNU GPL.

This app is online interface for FET Free Timetabling Software, user can register and create working table. User can enter all informations online and create timetable.
